## Page-by-Page Feature Plan

### Page 1: `index.html` — Home

**Hero section:**
- Full-viewport video background (100vw x 100vh)
- Dark gradient overlay
- Company name: "CORNERSTONE CONSTRUCTION CO." (small caps, letter-spaced, Archivo 600)
- Headline: "BUILT TO LAST." (Oswald 700, 96px desktop / 56px mobile, Off-White)
- Sub-headline: "Residential, commercial, and excavation services serving the region since 2003." (DM Sans, Warm Stone)
- Two CTAs: "View Our Projects" (amber fill) and "Get a Free Estimate" (amber outline)
- Scroll indicator (animated arrow bouncing gently)

**Stats bar** (below hero, amber accent band):
- Animated counters: `23+` Years in Business, `400+` Projects Completed, `98%` Client Satisfaction, `12` States Served
- Counter animation triggers when scrolled into view (IntersectionObserver + requestAnimationFrame)

**Services teaser** (3 cards):
- Home Building / Excavation / Commercial Construction
- Each card: icon (SVG), service name, one-liner, amber "Learn More" link to services.html
- On dark graphite surface, subtle border

**Featured Projects** (3 cards, 3-column grid):
- Project name, category tag (e.g., "Residential"), year, project image
- Hover: amber overlay + "View Project" CTA
- Links to projects.html

**Testimonials** (2 quotes):
- Client name, title/location, quote text
- Left amber border accent
- Clean sans-serif quote in italic DM Sans

**CTA banner:**
- Full-width amber band: "READY TO BUILD? LET'S TALK."
- Button: "Request a Free Estimate" (black on amber)

**Footer:**
- Logo + tagline
- Nav links (Home, Services, Projects, Contact)
- Contact info: phone, email, address
- Copyright

