## Navigation Design

**Desktop nav (sticky, top of page):**
- Logo left: "CORNERSTONE" (Oswald 700, amber) + "CONSTRUCTION CO." (DM Sans 500, Off-White)
- Links right: Home / Services / Projects / Contact
- Active page: amber underline
- Initial state on home page: transparent background; after 80px scroll: dark semi-opaque background (`rgba(13,15,18,0.95)`) with blur
- On all other pages: always solid dark background

**Mobile nav (breakpoint: 768px):**
- Hamburger icon (3 lines, morphs to X on open)
- Full-height slide-in menu from right (dark background)
- Large links, amber active state
- Closes on link click or outside tap

