## File Structure (8 files, well within 12-file cap)

```
../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/construction-company-website/
├── index.html          # Home page
├── services.html       # Services + pricing page
├── projects.html       # Projects gallery page
├── contact.html        # Contact form page
├── style.css           # All styles (vars, layout, components, pages, responsive)
├── main.js             # Nav, hamburger, scroll effects, shared IntersectionObserver setup
├── projects.js         # Filter logic + lightbox
└── contact.js          # Form validation + success state
```

Counter animation and hero video handling are inlined in `main.js` (small enough to not warrant separate files).

No bundler. No npm. Pure HTML/CSS/JS with Google Fonts loaded from CDN.

