## Proposal Guidance (for proposal-writer)

- **Demo name used in proposal:** "Cornerstone Construction Co. Website Demo"
- **Demo live URL:** `https://michaelwegter.com/demos/construction-company-website/`
- **Design system used in proposal one-pager and deck:** Match the demo palette (Charcoal Black `#0D0F12`, Safety Amber `#E8991A`, Off-White `#F0EDE8`, Gunmetal `#7A7F89`). Use Oswald for headings, DM Sans for body in the one-pager/deck.
- **Key selling points to emphasize:**
  1. Video-background homepage done right: smooth, legible, performant, with fallback.
  2. Pricing transparency on the services page (clients love seeing real numbers).
  3. Filterable project gallery: shows capability across all three service lines at once.
  4. Clean, industrial design with no template feel.
  5. Mobile-first responsive, WCAG AA accessible.
- **Michael's voice notes:** Direct, confident, shows genuine care for the client's business. Mention the "medium rare" brief and show you understood it. Reference specific pages of the demo by name.
